{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356930/extras/About_small.jpg?t=1717655538\" /><br>Roguebot is a fast-paced third person action-roguelite in which the player must fight their way to the top of a futuristic facility. Armed with a plethora of firearms and melee abilities you get to control a small robot on its journey through three distinct biomes. The deeply interwoven story unfolds as you find mysterious satellites that lie scattered in this ominous environment. No run is the same as the floors are procedurally created.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356930/extras/KeyFeaturesHeadline_small.jpg?t=1717655538\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">COMBAT SYSTEM</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fast paced action, by combining different types of ranged and melee attacks.<br></li><li> Responsive movement to dodge enemy attacks.<br></li><li> By collecting config shards after defeating bosses, you can unlock different abilites that influence many gameplay mechanics. </li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356930/extras/Fighting.gif?t=1717655538\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MODULAR EQUIPMENT</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Strategically decide what modifications to buy with machine parts dropped from enemies.<br></li><li> Freely combine over a dozen of equipment modifications with different rarities, allowing for high build variety.<br></li><li> Discover many synergies between different equipment mods and abilites.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356930/extras/Shop.gif?t=1717655538\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PROCEDURAL LEVELS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No run will be the same, each floor has a generated layout, with thoroughly thought out rules and conditions taken into account.<br></li><li> 3 distinct sections that differ in enemy types, level geometry,  environmental hazards and visual theme.<br></li><li> Each section is guarded by a unique boss fight.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356930/extras/Biomes.gif?t=1717655538\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356930/extras/Narrative_small.jpg?t=1717655538\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THEME AND LORE</h2><li> What starts out as an unassuming sci-fi game quickly turns into a discussion about morality and the human condition.<br></li><li> Read through three meticulously crafted stories of humans in the past. Unveil their fate as you go. <br></li><li> The cyclical nature of the Roguelite genre becomes a story-telling tool. <br></li><li> Learn more about the world and lore by talking to NPCs.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356930/extras/Story.gif?t=1717655538\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Who am I?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2356930/284a939fa1efe62fcd340c0f9ad4fc4e68260222.jpg"},{"name":"Nuke","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2356930/500a48e118ca2ae5cc2462a080710448ba303257.jpg"},{"name":"The cycle continues...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2356930/534e62e0241d2f954f538a0b57be24688962e064.jpg"},{"name":"Killing Spree","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2356930/27b2d4aadba3a6f4b5bd646cdd2f989d30478a31.jpg"},{"name":"Rampage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2356930/b62d16739079ea105dff1329e6dbe26d04a267ba.jpg"},{"name":"Unstoppable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2356930/3683670513526b510bcda2f56fba6d5